it.polimi.statemachine.states

Enum CHIAReplacementState

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<CHIAReplacementState>
      • it.polimi.statemachine.states.CHIAReplacementState
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    CHIAStateInterface, Serializable, Comparable<CHIAReplacementState>

    public enum CHIAReplacementState
extends Enum<CHIAReplacementState>
implements CHIAStateInterface
    represents a possible state of CHIA. It offers a method perform that given the current state and a CHIAAction returns the next state of the automaton.
    Author:
    Claudio Menghi
